    "Unsafe driving • Phones using -Right-handed texting (as shown below 'C1') -Right-handed phone conversation (as shown below 'C2') -Left-handed texting (as shown below 'C3') -Left-handed phone conversation (as shown below 'C4') • Entertainment system -Using the radio (as shown below 'C5') Fig. 5 Fig."
